Package alice.tuprolog.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicLibrary
    This class defines a set of basic built-in predicates for the tuProlog engine Library/Theory dependency: none
    ClassLoader
    used to load new classes without touching system class loader
    DCGLibrary
    Library for managing DCGs.
    EDCGLibrary
    Library for managing DCGs.
    IOLibrary
    This class provides basic I/O predicates.
    ISOIOLibrary
    This class provides basic ISO I/O predicates.
    ISOLibrary
    This class represents a tuProlog library providing most of the built-ins predicates and functors defined by ISO standard.
    JavaLibrary
    This class represents a tuProlog library enabling the interaction with the Java environment from tuProlog.
    ListenerInfo
    Information about an EventListener
    Signature
    Signature class mantains information about type and value of a method arguments
    TheoryLibrary
    Library built from Prolog theory.
